<a href="http://www.lemarin.fr/articles/detail/items/peche-illegale-au-senegal-le-chalutier-russe-a-pu-quitter-dakar.html" target="_self">http://www.lemarin.fr/articles/detail/items/peche-illegale-au-senegal-le...</a></p><p><i>Jeune Afrique</i>, Senegal: The fishing world prepares to take on pirate navies, 9 January 2014</p><p>
